<template>
 
      <b-container class="search">
        <b-row align-h="center">
          <b-col align-self="center" class="justify-content-center mb-3" lg="8">
            <b-form-input
              type="text"
              id="input-code"
              v-model="joinCode"
              placeholder="Enter Code"
            />
          </b-col>
        </b-row>

        <b-row align-h="center">
          <b-button variant="primary" @click="joinGame()">Go!</b-button>
        </b-row>
      </b-container>
 
</template>

<script>

export default {
  name: "GameJoin",
  data() {
    return {
      joinCode: ""
    };
  },

  methods: {
    joinGame() {
      if (this.joinCode != "") {
        this.$emit('code', this.joinCode);
      } else {
        alert("pls provide a code");
      }
    }
  }
};
</script>
